<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>86</hymn_number>
<title>HIDE ME, O MY SAVIOUR!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei selin, Aw ka Hukdampa,
 Na mun thiengtho ah;
 Na lopina lima chawlin,
 Na mel ei muhsak in.

[V2]
 Aw ei sel in!
 Aw Hukdampa, ei selin!
 Lalpa, ei vengin,
 Bittakin Na kawmah!

[V3]
 2. Ei selin, huihpi a nun tieng,
 Damsung tui lienah;
 Tui kinawk chungah khuva bang,
 Nang lam ei zawt sakin!

[V4]
 3. Ka lungkham laiin ei selin,
 Ka puokgik laiin;
 Kah laiin lungmuonna ka hawl,
 Nang mai nei piek theih chu.</lyrics>
</song>